### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE labeled_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    data VARCHAR(255),
    label VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE features (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feature_name VARCHAR(50),
    data_id INT REFERENCES labeled_data(id)
)

CREATE TABLE model (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(50),
    accuracy FLOAT
)

### STATEMENT

DELETE FROM labeled_data WHERE id = 1
